<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7732101>
    dc:description "FIGURE 10. Comparison of the presence or absence of spots and blotches inG.sardashtensis and G. kurdistanicus. Glyptothorax sardashtensis, from left: FCFUK 306, 51 mm SL; FCFUK 321, 45 mm SL; Lesser Zab, Iran. Glyptothorax kurdistanicus, from right: FCFUK 332, 67 mm SL; FCFUK 337, 43 mm SL; Lesser Zab, Iran." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7732101/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7732089>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Premaxillary tooth plate, nuchal plate, dentary elements, and vomer plate of G. kurdistanicus (A, C, E, and G respectively), FCFUK 338, 41 mm SL, and G. sardashtensis (B, D, F, and H respectively), FCFUK 314, 38 mm SL; a and b, ventral view of premaxillary tooth plate; c and d, dorsal view of the nuchal plate; e and f, dorsal view of dentary elements; g and h, ventral view of vomer plate. Abbreviations: ppe, premaxillary proximal element; pde, premaxillary distal element; anp, anterior nuchal plate; mnp, middle nuchal plate; pnp, posterior nuchal plate; spl, spinlet; fdr, first dorsal-fin ray; vt, villiform teeth; vp, vomerine plate; ps, posterior stem." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7732089/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7732103>
    dc:description "FIGURE 11. Pectoral-fin spine of Glyptothorax sardashtensis. From left to right FCFUK 320, 31 mm SL, FCFUK 314, 38 mm SL, and FCFUK 301, 58 mm SL. Numbers indicate the number posterior serrae, pink is the ossified part." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7732103/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7732107>
    dc:description "FIGURE 12. Glyptothorax kurdistanicus, upper row, from left: FCFUK 339, 27 mm SL; FCFUK 337, 43 mm SL; FCFUK 332, 67 mm SL; G. sardashtensis, lower row, from left: FCFUK 322, 21 mm SL; FSJF 4112, 52 mm SL; FCFUK 305, 55 mm SL; Lesser Zab, Iran." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7732107/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7732083>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Glyptothorax kurdistanicus, FCFUK 330, 108 mm SL; upper Lesser Zab, Iran." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7732083/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7732085>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Glyptothorax kurdistanicus, from left: FCFUK 330, 108 mm SL; FCFUK 333, 52 mm; SL; Lesser Zab, Iran." ;
